		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hey, Rai here. Lately, I've been working on a message box routine, which has mostly been programmed from scratch. <br /><br /><img src="http://i34.photobucket.com/albums/d122/Raides/text000_zpsbf0734eb.png" alt="Image" /><br /><br />It's not anywhere near done yet, but when it is, it will be very customizable.<br /><br />You'll be able to turn gradients on or off, choose from a variety of font sizes and be able to choose from static and scrolling text.<br /><br />I've even been thinking about doing an SNES-style RPG engine and may use this routine for it.

		

